          %small Version 0.10.1

%section.endorsements
  %h1 used by thousands of developers, including these fine companies:
  %ul.companies
    - for company, url in [["GitHub", "https://github.com"], ["Pinterest", "http://pinterest.com"], ["Heroku", "http://www.heroku.com"], ["Mutual Mobile", "http://www.mutualmobile.com"], ["Simple", "https://www.simple.com"]]
